        "description": "Immerse yourself in the exciting world of art with the VR game ARTPuzzle and collect jigsaw puzzles with iconic work by the most famous masters.\n\nExplore art galleries featuring paintings by artists of various eras, genres and countries, each with its own unique atmosphere and carefully selected paintings. Thanks to the great detail of the images, you will be able to pay attention to the smallest details of the paintings and reveal the author's idea in a new way.\n\nKey functions:\n- 9 different collections containing more than 50 puzzles\n- puzzles of various shapes and a wide range of difficulty levels\n- DLC collections: regular updates of new puzzles and collections\n\nARTPuzzle is not just a game, it is an educational journey that reveals art in a new way. Whether you are a lover of art or puzzles, or just looking for a unique and exciting experience, this game is sure to captivate and inspire you.\n",
